" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！</span></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔係遲左醒<br />\n而係一直都知, 但無人挑出黎講, 有共識唔講<br />\n因為呢啲涉及太多枱底野, 個啲野涉及太多政客同有頭有面既人<br />\nBIDEN家族一定唔係唯一, 過去十幾年, 有幾多人去過中國做生意, 比佢遊說過?個個都無拎野走? 個個都清白?<br />\n啲擁抱大熊貓派, 同背後啲金主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家爆係選戰姐, 同個勢要郁中共"},{"pid":"ee3ec62a68a85f3b4db284e22eed08fb08eabc22","tid":2265902,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:34:30.000Z","msg":"五毛水足<br />\n唔好理LEE個PO<br />\n推杜汶澤個分化PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb96b65f177b3b78e6ba482519ead80976686e0","tid":2265902,"uid":171313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"醒咗就要做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9491347e58afbdec4f7af5e9e891f4a981f54701","tid":2265902,"uid":7343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"中國成日話外國勢力<br />\n佢自己就係最強大外國勢力顛覆他人政府"},{"pid":"2eb8d882427f331ce8c4f33f612ccb5c07095f63","tid":2265902,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9491347e58afbdec4f7af5e9e891f4a981f54701","tid":2265902,"uid":7343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"中國成日話外國勢力<br />\n佢自己就係最強大外國勢力顛覆他人政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">開蝈呢幾十年黎，日日都好嬲好嬲好忙好忙，攪自己人又要攪人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"118a9bd116648c80482ff413f7ef40e495bc3e0c","tid":2265902,"uid":114781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:03:31.000Z","msg":"win-win means China win twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/